fulltitle: James Bamford: 'Body of Secrets' and the National Security Agency
title: James Bamford: 'Body of Secrets' and the National Security Agency
_filename: _James Bamford - 'Body of Secrets' and the National Security Agency.mp4
description:
JUNE 6, 2002 | Body of Secrets Mr. Bamford talked about the results of his research into the inner workings of the National Security Agency. His book is Body of Secrets: Anatomy of the Ultra-Secret National Security Agency, published by Anchor Books, is an investigative look into the behaviors of the NSA, as well as a closer look at the history and future of America’s espionage organization. Mr. Bamford said there should be congressional panels to monitor the agency. After the presentation, the author answered questions from members of the audience.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
